  <item nodeId="node-158">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine doctor's note</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A note from an appointment that reads: "severe case of amnesia, causing a memory loss of the past 2 weeks.". It's all a fog to me.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-159"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-159">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine old newspaper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A newspaper from 2 weeks ago with a disturbing front page... "Corruption may win - Jo&#x00E3;o and Maria Sapienze found dead in a dark alley". How can't I remember that day?&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-160"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-160">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine tablet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A tablet where I keep my diary... but for some reason the past 2 weeks have been erased... precisely the time I lost my memory... stupid thing, the first time it would actually be useful I forgot to write in it!&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-161"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-161">
    <command xml:space="preserve">open closet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">What a mess... well, look what we have here... this pile of paper has my current cases, and it's piling up... I should take a look at these.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-162"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-162">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine cases</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You can't see any such thing.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-163"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-163">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine pile of paper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">There are 2 cases here. Another couple just like my parents, found in Bingo Street... and a judge killed in his own chambers. He was working on some case about a cosmetics company.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-164"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-164">
    <command xml:space="preserve">leave</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">I could leave, but to where? I should probably read my cases first.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-165"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-165">
    <command xml:space="preserve">read cases</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You can't see any such thing.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
