  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-182">
    <command xml:space="preserve">go inside</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">&gt;A strange man bumps into you.&#x000A;Hey! Watch where you're going!&#x000A;He's already gone... could have at least apologized.&#x000A;&#x000A;El Court" Americano - Judge Richard's Office&#x000A;I remember hearing about this guy from my mother... I think they worked together on a couple of times...&#x000A;&#x000A;This is one small office... looks old, older than the rest of the building, like it's holding on to long forgotten past.&#x000A;&#x000A;It's well kept though, despite... everything.&#x000A;&#x000A;You can see a Fancy Desk (on which is an Open Letter), a Judge Richard's Dead Body, a Blood Stain and a Bookshelf here.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-183"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-183">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine blood stain</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">There's a trail of blood leading underneath the bookshelf.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
  </item>
