  <item nodeId="node-106">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine doctor's note</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A note from an appointment that reads: "severe case of amnesia, causing a memory loss of the past 2 weeks.". It's all a fog to me.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-107"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-107">
    <command xml:space="preserve">read doctor's note</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">There are more comments here... why did they perform an x-ray on me? I can't understand it.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-108"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-108">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine old newspaper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A newspaper from 2 weeks ago with a disturbing front page... "Corruption may win - Jo&#x00E3;o and Maria Alfonzo found dead in a dark alley". How can't I remember that day?&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-109"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-109">
    <command xml:space="preserve">read old newspaper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">My parents were pretty important in stopping the corruption in this city... I'm sure a lot of people would want them dead. It's not surprising this is in the cover of the newspaper... but I will find out who did this!&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-110"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-110">
    <command xml:space="preserve">read tablet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">What is wrong with me... I can't read this!&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-111"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-111">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine tablet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A tablet where I keep my diary... but for some reason the past 2 weeks have been erased... precisely the time I lost my memory...&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-112"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-112">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine closet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">You see nothing special about the closet.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-113"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-113">
    <command xml:space="preserve">open closet</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">What a mess... well, look what we have here... this pile of paper has my current cases, and it's piling up... I should take a look at these.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-114"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-114">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine pile of paper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">There are 2 cases here. Another couple just like my parents, found in Bingo Street... and a judge killed in his own chambers. He was working on some case about a cosmetics company.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-115"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-115">
    <command xml:space="preserve">read pile of paper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">The first case happened a week ago... they were found dead in a trash can. According to the police report, they had very peculiar injuries... it looks like they fought with the attacker.&#x000A;As for the second case, it was just delivered to me. The body is still in the courthouse, so I should head there soon. Judge Richard was found dead in his chambers found with a knife in his head. A judge can get a lot of enemies, but he was only working on one case at the time... I should go there.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-116"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-116">
    <command xml:space="preserve">leave</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">It's chilly outside. I should probably wear a hat.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-117"/>
    </children>
