  <item nodeId="node-135">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine lady</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">This lady seems competent. And she is typing so fast too. And cute too. Maybe I can ask her out on a date after I solve this case.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-136"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-136">
    <command xml:space="preserve">talk to lady</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Hello, may I know where Judge Richard's chambers are?&#x000A;"I'm sorry, but he is quite busy at the moment, you need to return another day."&#x000A;I am Detective Alfonzo. I was called here to investigate his death.&#x000A;"My apologies... it's that room to the right."&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-137"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-137">
    <command xml:space="preserve">talk to lady</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">"The Judge was a good man. He was always fair in his trials. Why would someone kill him?..."&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-138"/>
    </children>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-138">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine statue</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">They sure have the budget... but why is the lady blind? Weird stuff.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-139"/>
    </children>
  </item>
